### Hadith 1:196

*Narrated 'Abdullah bin Zaid:*

Once Allah's Apostle came to us and we brought out water for him in a
brass pot. He performed ablution thus: He washed his face thrice, and
his forearms to the elbows twice, then passed his wet hands lightly over
the head from front to rear and brought them to front again and washed
his feet (up to the ankles).

